    {
      "id": "PopularPost270381",
      "post_content": "So this is definitely a card. Yup. It's a card alright. That being said, it could have easily costed R1 and not been overpowered. Why, just look at [Searing Spear](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Searing Spear), another burn spell that only sees marginal play. There's so much design space that could be utilized, but WotC seems content to unsuccessfully reinvent the Lightning Bolt over and over again. With the new [Lotleth Troll](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lotleth Troll), I'd even be happy to see [Incinerate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Incinerate) back.",
      "posted_by": "Eternal_Blue",
