    {
      "id": "PopularPost283538",
      "post_content": "[Annihilating Fire](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Annihilating Fire) does exactly what it needs to do in the current standard format. It kills [Thragtusk](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name= Thragtusk). It kills the endless stream of Centaurs. It deals with the limitless numbers of 3/3's in this format, AS well as the zombies in the format -  [Pillar of Flame](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name= Pillar of Flame) can't do both. I run a few sideboard, sometimes mainboard if i expect a lot of junk, jund, or well.. green.   \n  \n4/5 - it's cost means that you have to run red heavy, but it does definitely pull it's weight, and that is what counts.  \n  ",
